=  Fast setup of a Java Microservie project with MicroProfileStarter 
Thomas Südbröcker<https://github.com/thomassuedbroecker>

Thomas Südbröcker shows the easy setup of an own MicroProfile/OpenLiberty project with MicroProfileStarter. He has created a 60-90 minute hands-on workshop microservice development with MicroProfile/OpenLiberty and the deployment to Kubernetes on IBM Cloud.
